1
00:00:07,100 --> 00:00:10,340
[The Glory of Queen]

2
00:00:10,340 --> 00:00:13,500
[Episode 1]

3
00:00:15,220 --> 00:00:19,960
[House of Nanfeng]

4
00:00:20,940 --> 00:00:23,500
In the Yuezun Kingdom,
women hold power over men.

5
00:00:23,900 --> 00:00:26,180
Women take the lead in public affairs,
serving as officials and merchants,

6
00:00:26,580 --> 00:00:28,780
while men attend to matters
within the household.

7
00:00:29,220 --> 00:00:31,540
All decisions rest in women's hands.

8
00:00:32,460 --> 00:00:35,460
And, a man's greatest honor
is to wed a high-born woman,

9
00:00:35,820 --> 00:00:38,580
to support his wife in her endeavors
and help raise their daughters.

10
00:00:40,420 --> 00:00:42,140
Excellent dancing.
You shall be rewarded.

11
00:00:42,420 --> 00:00:44,740
- Splendid!
- Well performed!

12
00:00:44,740 --> 00:00:46,140
You shall be rewarded.

13
00:00:47,660 --> 00:00:49,870
The Pei family of Qinghe
is the foremost clan

14
00:00:49,870 --> 00:00:50,820
in fragrance-making.

15
00:00:52,180 --> 00:00:56,460
Legend has it that they possess
a famed fragrance manual

16
00:00:56,460 --> 00:00:57,740
of inestimable value.

17
00:00:58,340 --> 00:01:00,810
For years,
countless have tried to obtain it,

18
00:01:00,810 --> 00:01:02,140
but none have succeeded.

19
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:09,980
How audacious of you

20
00:01:09,980 --> 00:01:11,820
to dare steal from our master!

21
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:15,660
Fools that we are,
we failed to recognize the chief

22
00:01:15,900 --> 00:01:17,500
and have now committed an offense.

23
00:01:17,860 --> 00:01:19,740
Please spare our lives.

24
00:01:19,980 --> 00:01:21,260
I may spare your lives,

25
00:01:21,500 --> 00:01:22,980
provided you do one thing for us.

26
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:25,420
Steal the Pei family's fragrance manual,

27
00:01:25,820 --> 00:01:27,340
and you shall be spared.

28
00:01:27,340 --> 00:01:29,480
[Song Zhiyao]

29
00:01:29,780 --> 00:01:31,020
Shut up! Don't try anything funny!

30
00:01:31,420 --> 00:01:32,100
Ergou.

31
00:01:33,020 --> 00:01:34,660
You have five days.

32
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:37,420
If you fail, the next time we meet,

33
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:40,100
what you see
will be their severed heads.

34
00:01:42,940 --> 00:01:45,940
A thief! After them! Hurry!

35
00:01:47,740 --> 00:01:49,140
Quick! They fled that way!

36
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:51,020
Go!

37
00:01:52,180 --> 00:01:52,620
This way!

38
00:01:57,020 --> 00:01:58,340
They were just here. Where did they go?

39
00:01:58,660 --> 00:01:59,300
[Fragrance Manual]
Did they go into

40
00:01:59,300 --> 00:01:59,940
the Second Young Master's room?

41
00:01:59,980 --> 00:02:00,500
Check over there.

42
00:02:00,660 --> 00:02:01,140
All right.

43
00:02:01,900 --> 00:02:02,420
Let's go!

44
00:02:05,140 --> 00:02:05,700
There's no one here.

45
00:02:05,980 --> 00:02:06,540
Come!

46
00:02:13,420 --> 00:02:15,220
My Lady, something has happened
in the manor.

47
00:02:17,060 --> 00:02:19,140
The fragrance manual was stolen
from the Tianshu Pavilion.

48
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:24,480
[Pei Xiuning]
[Acting Matriarch of the Pei Manor]

49
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:28,440
[Feng Lusheng]
[Pei Xiuning's Husband]

50
00:02:28,780 --> 00:02:30,420
The manor
has been completely sealed off.

51
00:02:31,060 --> 00:02:32,220
We have searched everywhere,

52
00:02:33,420 --> 00:02:34,260
except…

53
00:02:34,940 --> 00:02:36,020
Except where?

54
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:42,660
Except for Second Young Master
Pei Jingheng's courtyard,

55
00:02:43,100 --> 00:02:43,740
am I right?

56
00:02:44,700 --> 00:02:45,300
Yes.

57
00:02:46,420 --> 00:02:47,220
Outrageous!

58
00:02:48,060 --> 00:02:49,980
The fragrance manual
is the Pei family's greatest treasure.

59
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:52,740
Hidden with such care,
yet it was still stolen.

60
00:02:53,580 --> 00:02:55,460
Should it suffer
even the slightest damage,

61
00:02:55,940 --> 00:02:58,980
how are we to face our ancestors?

62
00:02:59,540 --> 00:03:00,620
[Pei Qingshan]
[Lord of the Pei Manor]

63
00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:01,620
Where is Xiuning?

64
00:03:04,380 --> 00:03:05,820
She may already have retired
for the night,

65
00:03:06,100 --> 00:03:06,980
but I have already sent...

66
00:03:07,060 --> 00:03:08,580
There is no need for you
to trouble yourself.

67
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:12,620
I have already sent more men

68
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:14,660
to capture the thief.

69
00:03:18,740 --> 00:03:19,940
Rest assured, Mother.

70
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:21,740
The manor is heavily guarded.

71
00:03:22,940 --> 00:03:26,420
That petty thief will not escape.

72
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:29,940
You reek of liquor.

73
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:32,180
It was only a small indulgence.

74
00:03:33,140 --> 00:03:36,180
I entrusted you with the duties
of acting matriarch of the household,

75
00:03:36,700 --> 00:03:38,820
not so you could indulge yourself.

76
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:41,820
If you fail to recover
the fragrance manual,

77
00:03:41,980 --> 00:03:43,220
hand back the family seal!

78
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,260
[Pei Songrong]
[Matriarch of the Pei Manor]

79
00:03:45,260 --> 00:03:47,060
Capture the thief!

80
00:03:49,060 --> 00:03:49,900
I think they headed that way.

81
00:04:06,660 --> 00:04:10,500
[Pei Jingheng]
[Second Young Master of the Pei Manor]

82
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:11,780
Why are you just standing there?

83
00:04:12,820 --> 00:04:13,980
Hold on, everyone. Stay put.

84
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:15,740
Xiuning,

85
00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:17,300
Jingheng never welcomes outsiders

86
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:18,900
into his courtyard,

87
00:04:18,900 --> 00:04:19,780
except me, his father.

88
00:04:20,460 --> 00:04:21,580
Perhaps I should go check first.

89
00:04:27,620 --> 00:04:28,380
Jingheng.

90
00:04:28,820 --> 00:04:29,460
It's me, your father.

91
00:04:30,060 --> 00:04:31,180
Someone broke into the manor.

92
00:04:31,460 --> 00:04:33,220
They seem to be making their way
to your courtyard,

93
00:04:33,620 --> 00:04:34,660
so I've come to see if you're safe.

94
00:04:34,660 --> 00:04:35,380
Are you all right?

95
00:04:35,660 --> 00:04:36,300
Father,

96
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:38,300
there are no intruders here.

97
00:04:39,500 --> 00:04:41,820
That's good. Get some rest early.

98
00:04:42,060 --> 00:04:42,780
Don't stay up too late.

99
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:46,500
Xiuning, Jingheng says

100
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:47,740
there are no intruders here.

101
00:04:47,820 --> 00:04:48,540
Relax.

102
00:04:49,260 --> 00:04:50,380
No need to worry, everyone.

103
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:51,340
You may leave.

104
00:05:03,860 --> 00:05:04,500
Search the area!

105
00:05:18,100 --> 00:05:20,060
Aunt, may I ask what brings you here
at this late hour?

106
00:05:20,900 --> 00:05:22,060
There's a thief in the manor.

107
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:25,180
The servants say
they're heading for your courtyard.

108
00:05:26,020 --> 00:05:27,980
I'm worried about you,
so I came to take a look.

109
00:05:28,260 --> 00:05:30,740
I appreciate your concern, Aunt.
There's no thief here.

110
00:05:31,420 --> 00:05:32,420
If you don't believe me,

111
00:05:32,460 --> 00:05:34,180
please feel free to search my room.

112
00:05:35,340 --> 00:05:36,060
All right, now.

113
00:05:36,140 --> 00:05:37,780
Jingheng, since you're safe,
we're all relieved.

114
00:05:38,140 --> 00:05:39,220
We'll be leaving now.

115
00:05:40,380 --> 00:05:41,980
Let's go. Time to leave.

116
00:05:58,060 --> 00:05:59,980
I'm sorry. I am truly sorry.

117
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:01,420
Who sent you?

118
00:06:01,700 --> 00:06:03,380
And what are you doing in my room?

119
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:05,420
I must not mention the fragrance manual.

120
00:06:07,580 --> 00:06:09,740
No one sent me.

121
00:06:13,020 --> 00:06:13,860
Listen,

122
00:06:14,900 --> 00:06:15,940
my patience

123
00:06:18,140 --> 00:06:19,060
is running out.

124
00:06:19,060 --> 00:06:20,460
I'm nothing but a mere thief.

125
00:06:20,460 --> 00:06:22,620
I only came to the Pei Manor
to steal a bit of food.

126
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:24,060
She is different from

127
00:06:24,060 --> 00:06:25,980
the assassins my aunt sent before.

128
00:06:26,420 --> 00:06:27,940
She carries no weapons,

129
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:29,900
and her skill is rudimentary at best.

130
00:06:30,780 --> 00:06:31,740
But I must find out

131
00:06:32,060 --> 00:06:33,700
why she has come here

132
00:06:33,900 --> 00:06:35,260
before letting her leave.

133
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:40,820
Second Young Master, you're really kind

134
00:06:41,980 --> 00:06:43,540
to let me change my wet clothes.

135
00:06:43,940 --> 00:06:45,220
You're handsome and good-hearted.

136
00:06:45,780 --> 00:06:46,700
From today on,

137
00:06:46,820 --> 00:06:48,700
I'll do everything I can to repay you.

138
00:06:50,940 --> 00:06:52,740
All right, from today on,

139
00:06:52,980 --> 00:06:54,780
you'll serve in my courtyard.

140
00:06:57,940 --> 00:06:58,620
Serve the tea.

141
00:06:59,260 --> 00:06:59,860
On it.

142
00:07:10,660 --> 00:07:11,900
The tea is here, Second Young Master.

143
00:07:14,820 --> 00:07:15,380
Enjoy it.

144
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:28,420
Here's a warning.

145
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:29,820
Don't try to run away.

146
00:07:30,220 --> 00:07:32,420
Don't worry.
I definitely won't run away.

147
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:42,380
You...

148
00:07:47,460 --> 00:07:48,420
Please.

149
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:52,300
I rule Eighteen‑Li Alley, all right.

150
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:54,740
You think a pampered young master
like you can trap me?

151
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:58,580
Dagou, Ergou,

152
00:07:59,020 --> 00:07:59,940
Wu, Liu,

153
00:08:00,180 --> 00:08:01,460
I'm going to save you.

154
00:08:05,060 --> 00:08:06,060
Why do I feel so dizzy?

155
00:08:23,260 --> 00:08:26,260
You've only been managing the household
for just over a month,

156
00:08:26,820 --> 00:08:28,740
and look at the mess you've made.

157
00:08:29,700 --> 00:08:31,020
Hand back

158
00:08:31,740 --> 00:08:33,580
the Pei family seal today.

159
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:38,100
Mother, that petty thief
who stole the fragrance manual

160
00:08:38,460 --> 00:08:40,620
went straight
for the manor's secret chamber

161
00:08:41,220 --> 00:08:42,580
and succeeded on the first try.

162
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:50,380
Tell me,
how could such a coincidence occur?

163
00:08:53,460 --> 00:08:54,260
Jingheng.

164
00:08:59,580 --> 00:09:00,260
Grandmother.

165
00:09:00,980 --> 00:09:02,060
From today on,

166
00:09:02,260 --> 00:09:05,180
all matters of the household
and the fragrance shop

167
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:07,300
are entrusted to you.

168
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:12,220
I am the eldest legitimate daughter!

169
00:09:12,740 --> 00:09:14,380
Mother, are you really going to
hand the family over

170
00:09:14,380 --> 00:09:15,340
to this man?

171
00:09:15,340 --> 00:09:16,060
Impudent!

172
00:09:17,380 --> 00:09:19,660
Jingheng's talent
in fragrance-making is unmatched.

173
00:09:20,060 --> 00:09:22,180
He will surely elevate
the Pei family's craft

174
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:23,980
and secure its fame for eternity.

175
00:09:24,260 --> 00:09:24,980
But you,

176
00:09:25,460 --> 00:09:28,140
in your short time in charge,
have lost the fragrance manual.

177
00:09:28,620 --> 00:09:30,380
A blunder like this

178
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:32,620
has never happened in our family.

179
00:09:32,820 --> 00:09:34,380
If the manual can't be recovered…

180
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:35,860
If the manual can't be recovered,

181
00:09:36,980 --> 00:09:38,700
you can punish me as you see fit.

182
00:09:43,700 --> 00:09:46,180
So it was the fragrance manual
that was stolen last night.

183
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:06,720
♪The secret about you
is buried deep in my heart♪

184
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:13,160
♪I draw near, then pull away, fearing
I might yield to this attraction♪

185
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:17,160
♪I like to think I'm keeping my cool♪

186
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:19,960
♪But my instincts
keep pulling me closer♪

187
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:26,760
♪Unwittingly,
I've fallen completely for you♪

188
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:33,120
♪Can the sacrifices of this life
measure the depth of love?♪

189
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:39,720
♪It's too late to summon the courage
to hold you once more♪

190
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:43,520
♪Having witnessed
all the world's splendor♪

191
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:46,280
♪I've felt joy and sorrow
for one soul alone♪

192
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:52,520
♪For our kindred souls,
all I can give is this humble heart♪

193
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:56,360
♪If I encounter you in this life♪

194
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:59,080
♪Fate is already fulfilled♪

195
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:05,500
♪Let this chapter become a memory,
breaking free from destiny♪

196
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:12,280
♪In the next life,
may the course of time lead me to you♪

197
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:18,880
♪With a sincere heart,
I shall carry our love forward♪
